title: Low Cholesterol Cookbook by Shasta Press
description:
The Low-Cholesterol Cookbook & Health Plan will make it easy for you to achieve low cholesterol by helping you make smart changes to your diet. The innovative low-cholesterol "1 + 1 - 1 Eating Plan" will show you how to choose the best low-cholesterol foods, how to add foods that increase good cholesterol, and how to subtract the ones that increase bad cholesterol. 

With more than100 quick and simple-to-follow, low-cholesterol recipes, and a no-nonsense guide to understanding what your cholesterol numbers mean, this unique cookbook and health guide will give you a practical eating program to help you see amazing results.

Genre: Non-Fiction, Cookery
